  Example usage:

  <xsd:import namespace="http://jdtaus.org/core/model"
              schemaLocation="http://sites.jdtaus.org/jdtaus-core/1.0.x/jdtaus-core-schemas/jdtaus-core-1.0.xsd" />

  The recommended namespace prefix is "core".]]>
    </xsd:documentation>
